    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>This video will be showcasing Virtual Cash Terminals (VCTs), including:</p><ul><li><p>Opening a VCT</p></li><li><p>Viewing a current VCT</p></li><li><p>Closing a VCT</p></li></ul><a class=\"external-link\" data-card-appearance=\"embed\" data-layout=\"center\" data-original-height=\"480.00\" data-original-width=\"853.34\" data-width=\"100.00\" href=\"https://youtu.be/MMlulRD6XYI\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://youtu.be/MMlulRD6XYI</a><h2 id=\"VirtualCashTerminals(VCTs)(video)-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933901843/Virtual+Cash+Terminal+VCT+Setup\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933901843\" data-linked-resource-version=\"16\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Setting up a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT)</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933639827/Assign+a+Virtual+Cash+Terminal+VCT+to+Accept+Payments\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933639827\" data-linked-resource-version=\"22\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Starting a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT) to Accept Payments</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933541639/Close+Reconcile+a+Virtual+Cash+Terminal\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933541639\" data-linked-resource-version=\"10\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Closing a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT)</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934229524/Reports+Cash+Reconciliation\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934229524\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Reports: Cash Reconciliation</a></p>",
